<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/29 (Thu) 10 Benefits of Traveling/9 Proven Time Management Techniques and Tools | USAHS (Host: Joyce)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=684&amp;p=712#p712"><![CDATA[
12/29 (Thu) 10 Benefits of Traveling/9 Proven Time Management Techniques and Tools | USAHS (Host: Joyce)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session1: 10 Benefits of Traveling<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://skyrefund.com/en/blog/benefits-of-travelling#:~:text=The%20importance%20of%20travel%20ranges%20from%20lower%20chances,your%20creativity%2C%20your%20sense%20of%20happiness%20and%20satisfaction">https://skyrefund.com/en/blog/benefits- ... tisfaction</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you think a post-pandemic recovery in tourism will risk faltering as the global economy loses momentum amid the energy shock, high inflation?<br />2.What are the advantages of travelling? Why is travelling important?<br />3.Could you come up with some travel-related adventures that not only sounded exciting , but are also doable for many people?<br />4.Please talk about your most unforgettable travel experiences that you had been to?<br />5.Do you have any travel ideas swirling through your mind? How do you finally build your travel bucket list?<br /><br /><br />Session 2: Proven Time Management Techniques and Tools | USAHS<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.usa.edu/blog/time-management-techniques/">https://www.usa.edu/blog/time-management-techniques/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Why do we need to maintain a work-life balance? Is it really that important?<br />2.Are you struggling to cram everything on your plate into a day's time?<br />3.How to manage your time to achieve work life balance and ensure emotional well-being?<br />4.Could you share some time management tips that actually work?<br />5.What are advantages of good Time Management?...<br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Dec 23, 2022 2:54 pm</p><hr />
